@startuml
participant "Customer Service" as CS
participant "Catalog Service" as CAS
participant "Order Service" as OS
queue "RabbitMQ" as RMQ

== Customer Creation ==
CS -> CS: Create Customer
CS -> RMQ: Publish CustomerCreated event
RMQ -> OS: Consume CustomerCreated event
OS -> OS: Update local customer registry

== Catalog Item Creation ==
CAS -> CAS: Create Catalog Item
CAS -> RMQ: Publish CatalogItemCreated event
RMQ -> OS: Consume CatalogItemCreated event
OS -> OS: Update local catalog registry

== Order Creation ==
OS -> OS: Create Order
OS -> RMQ: Publish OrderCreated event
RMQ -> CS: Consume OrderCreated event
CS -> CS: Update customer order history

== Order Update ==
OS -> OS: Update Order
OS -> RMQ: Publish OrderUpdated event
RMQ -> CS: Consume OrderUpdated event
CS -> CS: Update customer order history

== Order Removal ==
OS -> OS: Remove Order
OS -> RMQ: Publish OrderRemoved event
RMQ -> CS: Consume OrderRemoved event
CS -> CS: Update customer order history

== Health Check ==
CS -> CS: Perform health check
CAS -> CAS: Perform health check
OS -> OS: Perform health check
@enduml